{
  "stem": "4113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then I also found out my father was crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was screaming get me because why am I pouring salt in his wounds because I was yelling at him, how come you let them go without me knowing?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I would've inquired first, you know, to find out what's going to be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Well, anyway, that same day, my cousin's, my half cousins who worked for us, his wife comes back from that transport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And she told the story what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They loaded them on the trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as they were transporting them, a flat tire-- they got a flat tire on that truck-- on one of the few tucks that my mother and my sister were on, and she was on.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So had them get off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they stood by the side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother went over to Schmatsler and told him, Herr Schmatsler, you know, I am the glasermeister's wife.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She described that story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he hit her in the face and told her to get back in line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, whether he did it because other Gestapo were there, you know, I have a feeling that he probably would have let her go if there weren't others there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she and a number of peasants were coming and going towards our town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this cousin's wife of mine hooked herself on to those peasants and came back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is how we found out what happened with that transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then came the fateful day December 4, 1942-- the night before it was announced that the ghetto is now going to be completely liquidated.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I have to tell you something else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My younger brother, one year younger, they needed to some Jews to clean up after a ghetto that was liquidated, the Jaslo, where the headquarters of the Gestapo was.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
